<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Hire Start Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }

        .info {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        a {
            color: #28a745;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>🧑‍💼 New Hire Starting</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong>TTO Logistics Team</strong>,</p>
        <p>This is a reminder that a new hire will start with your team at <strong>{{WarehouseName}}</strong>.</p>

        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>👤 Applicant Details:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{Name}} {{LastName}}</li>
                <li><strong>Position:</strong> {{Position}}</li>
                <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{ApplicantPhone}}</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ApplicantEmail}}">{{ApplicantEmail}}</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>🗓 Start Details:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{StartDate}} ({{StartWeekday}})</li>
                <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{StartTime}}</li>
               
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Please ensure onboarding steps are ready (badge, route assignment, training, paperwork).</p>

     
        <p class="footer">
            Regards,<br />
            <strong>TTO Logistics HR System</strong><br />
            📧 <a href="mailto:support@ttologistics.com">support@ttologistics.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

